==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Slatting
<hw>Slat"ting</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The violent shaking or flapping
of anything hanging loose in the wind, as of a sail, when being hauled
down.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

